OL,3,CApril weather has been a 'month of two
OL,4,Chalves' Met Office says
OL,6,FWhen asked why people may feel it's
OL,7,Fbeen colder than expected for
OL,8,Fspringtime, despite temperatures
OL,9,Fsuggesting otherwise, Ms Bokota
OL,10,Freplied: "The last couple of weeks has
OL,11,Fjust been quite cooler than average."
OL,13,FShe continued: "It's been quite a dull
OL,14,Fmonth ` duller than it should be on
OL,15,Faverage ` so there's been less
OL,16,Fsunshine around, so that kind of
OL,17,Fimpacts what people feel with the
OL,18,Fweather as well.
