OL,3,CApril weather has been a 'month of two
OL,4,Chalves' Met Office says
OL,6,F"It's been mainly unsettled and
OL,7,Fchangeable, so I think that just sort
OL,8,Fof feeds into people's interpretation
OL,9,Fof what the weather feels like."
OL,11,FThe meteorologist said that although
OL,12,Fthe forecast next week is looking
OL,13,Fwarmer from Wednesday, it might not be
OL,14,Fthe "glorious heatwave" people are
OL,15,Fhoping for ahead of the May bank
OL,16,Fholiday weekend.
